## Performance and License

Madoko is a javascript program (written in [Koka]) that runs on [Node.js]. It is about 30% faster
then [Marked] \(one of the fastest Javascript markdown implementations), and
about 6 to 8 times faster than [Showdown] and [Markdown.js]. Madoko is also
available as a .NET executable on windows.

Madoko is free software available under the [Apache 2.0 license] at [madoko.codeplex.com].

